name: 102GNM1000
short_description:
• For use in residential wiring as branch circuits for outlets, switches and other loads
  • Rated at 600 volts
  • Designed for exposed and concealed applications in normally dry locations at temperatures not to exceed 194 degrees Fahrenheit (with amperage limited to taht for 140 degrees Fahrenheit conductors), as specified in the National Electrical Code 1

  • 100 ft. long

  • Includes ground wire
  • Annealed soft copper conductors
  • UL listed
  • Note: Product may vary by store
